
  TEMPEST

  The TEMPEST task is an iterative process director that reads the BMP180 and
  sends the values to an output device in a BAROMETER_NOTIFY message.

  The output device is selected by:-
         send_SET_IOCTL(TEMPEST, SIOC_SELECT_OUTPUT, selection);
         1: SARK
         2: JIRA
         3: PERU
         7: GENERAL CALL
     
